articles.title: Women's ODIs: India drop catches as Australia seal the match and series - Hindustan Times
articles.description: The hosts, needing to win to stay in the series, dropped seven catches to let their formidable rivals off the hook at the Wankhede Stadium | Cricket
articles.content: When Amol Muzumdar addressed his first press conference as India head coach in early December, he picked fielding as one of his top priorities. In that regard, his teams performance on Saturday would… [+2909 chars]
